Description:
   Sanctified Strike delivers a melee attack infused with holy power that
   simultaneously heals the Templar for a portion of the damage dealt. This
   represents the integrated combat-and-consecration methodology that
   emerged from the garrison crisis -- "striking techniques that
   incorporated consecration effects."

   Costs: Movement (via subtract_energy_cost)
   Cooldown: 15 rounds
   Damage element: Physical + Holy
   Damage formula: war_attack base * (10 + Templar level) / 10
   Self-heal: damage dealt / 5

   Distinct from Holystrike (pure holy damage, combo-compatible). Sanctified
   Strike trades combo integration for self-sustain, reflecting the
   Templar's dual-function doctrine.
